            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1940-11-28T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1940-11-28T00:00:00-05:00" n="744"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d744">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.248/194</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Memorandum of Conversation, by the Secretary of State</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1940-11-28">November 28,
                            1940</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Dr. Soong came in at his request. He desired to follow up his application for a
                    loan and for more airplanes, by handing to me a confidential communication,
                    unsigned, from Chiang Kai-shek, to be transmitted to the President (copy
                        attached),<note n="13" xml:id="d744fn13">
                        <hi rend="italic">Infra.</hi>
                    </note> I shall today hand it to the President.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>C[<hi rend="smallcaps">ordell</hi>] H[<hi rend="smallcaps"
                        >ull</hi>]</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
